  <brief_title>Influence of Hepatic Impairment on Pharmacokinetic (PK) and Pharmacodynamic (PD) of Gemigliptin PK and PD After Multiple Oral Doses in Healthy White Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-center, Open-label Trial, Investigating the Pharmacokinetics, Pharmacodynamics and the Safety Profile After a Single Oral Dose of Gemigliptin (Investigational Product) in Healthy Subjects and Subjects With Mild or Moderate Hepatic Impairment and After Multiple Oral Dose in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
