  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The trial will investigate the influence of hepatic function on the PK of gemigliptin. In an
      additional treatment period, the PK and safety of multiple dosing of gemigliptin in healthy
      White subjects will be investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
